cards.name: Karn Liberated
cards.oracle_text:
+4: Target player exiles a card from their hand.
−3: Exile target permanent.
−14: Restart the game, leaving in exile all non-Aura permanent cards exiled with Karn Liberated. Then put those cards onto the battlefield under your control.

cards.name: A-Elderleaf Mentor
cards.oracle_text: When Elderleaf Mentor enters the battlefield, create a 1/1 green Elf Warrior creature token.

cards.name: Davriel, Soul Broker
cards.oracle_text:
+1: Until your next turn, whenever an opponent attacks you and/or planeswalkers you control, they discard a card. If they can't, they sacrifice an attacking creature.
−2: Accept one of Davriel's offers, then accept one of Davriel's conditions.
−3: Target creature an opponent controls perpetually gets -3/-3.

cards.oracle_text:
Flying, vigilance, haste
Whenever Velomachus Lorehold attacks, look at the top seven cards of your library. You may cast an instant or sorcery spell with mana value less than or equal to Velomachus Lorehold's power from among them without paying its mana cost. Put the rest on the bottom of your library in a random order.

cards.name: Sea Drake
cards.oracle_text:
Flying
When Sea Drake enters the battlefield, return two target lands you control to their owner's hand.

cards.name: Cleaver Riot
cards.oracle_text: Creatures you control gain double strike until end of turn. (They deal both first-strike and regular combat damage.)
cards.flavor_text: Measure once, cut twice.

cards.name: Alaborn Grenadier
cards.oracle_text: Vigilance
cards.flavor_text:
"Ever proud, ever vigilant."
—Grenadier motto

cards.flavor_text: It hunts with unnerving ferocity.

cards.oracle_text:
Flash
Enchant creature

cards.oracle_text: {X}, {T}: Target creature with power X or less can't be blocked this turn.
cards.flavor_text: Woven from threads of the spirit world, the mistcloak rendered its wearer invisible, but quickly fell to tatters.

cards.name: Amrou Kithkin
cards.oracle_text: Amrou Kithkin can't be blocked by creatures with power 3 or greater.
cards.flavor_text: Quick and agile, Amrou Kithkin can usually escape from even the most fearsome opponents.

cards.oracle_text: When Conclave Naturalists enters the battlefield, you may destroy target artifact or enchantment.
cards.flavor_text: "Your swords and wards have no power here."

cards.name: Ajani's Influence
cards.oracle_text:
Put two +1/+1 counters on target creature.
Look at the top five cards of your library. You may reveal a white card from among them and put it into your hand. Put the rest on the bottom of your library in a random order.

cards.name: Forbidden Orchard
cards.oracle_text:
{T}: Add one mana of any color.
Whenever you tap Forbidden Orchard for mana, target opponent creates a 1/1 colorless Spirit creature token.

cards.name: Migratory Greathorn
cards.oracle_text:
Mutate {2}{G} (If you cast this spell for its mutate cost, put it over or under target non-Human creature you own. They mutate into the creature on top plus all abilities from under it.)
Whenever this creature mutates, search your library for a basic land card, put it onto the battlefield tapped, then shuffle.

cards.name: Eye of Singularity
cards.oracle_text:
When Eye of Singularity enters the battlefield, destroy each permanent with the same name as another permanent, except for basic lands. They can't be regenerated.
Whenever a permanent other than a basic land enters the battlefield, destroy all other permanents with that name. They can't be regenerated.

cards.name: Skyclave Relic
cards.oracle_text:
Kicker {3}
Indestructible
When Skyclave Relic enters the battlefield, if it was kicked, create two tapped tokens that are copies of Skyclave Relic.
{T}: Add one mana of any color.
cards.flavor_text: Skyclaves held the key to reshaping the world.

cards.name: Water Gun Balloon Game
cards.oracle_text:
As Water Gun Balloon Game enters the battlefield, each player puts a pop! counter on "0."
Whenever a player casts a spell, move that player's pop! counter up one.
Whenever a player's pop! counter hits "5," that player creates a 5/5 pink Giant Teddy Bear creature token and resets all pop! counters to "0."

cards.name: Folk of An-Havva
cards.oracle_text: Whenever Folk of An-Havva blocks, it gets +2/+0 until end of turn.
cards.flavor_text:
"There are those who accept being told what to do, what to think, and what to say. Then there are the Folk of An-Havva."
—Reyhan, Samite Alchemist

cards.name: Stonerise Spirit
cards.oracle_text:
Flying
{4}, Exile a card from your graveyard: Target creature gains flying until end of turn.

cards.name: Silver Knight
cards.oracle_text: First strike, protection from red

Deathtouch

cards.oracle_text:
Flying
Undying (When this creature dies, if it had no +1/+1 counters on it, return it to the battlefield under its owner's control with a +1/+1 counter on it.)

Ninjutsu {2}{U} ({2}{U}, Return an unblocked attacker you control to hand: Put this card onto the battlefield from your hand tapped and attacking.)
Whenever Mist-Syndicate Naga deals combat damage to a player, create a token that's a copy of Mist-Syndicate Naga.

cards.name: Subcontract
cards.oracle_text: A person outside the game looks at target opponent's hand and chooses a nonland card from it. That player discards that card.
cards.flavor_text: Martha was in and out in exactly two minutes—thirty seconds to administer the poison plus a minute and a half to properly refold the napkins.

cards.name: Tainted Well
cards.oracle_text:
Enchant land
When Tainted Well enters the battlefield, draw a card.
Enchanted land is a Swamp.
cards.flavor_text:
"No, *you* get the water. I ain't thirsty."
—Squee

Flying
